name: TURGUT ALP AXE
description:
The Turgut Alp 100% Original Axe From Dirilis Ertugrul. 
Dirilis Axe is comes from famous Turkish series called Dirilis Ertugrul. 
Turgut Alp Who lived for 125 years! He was one of the warriors and Alps who fought for Ertuğrul, a Turkic leader and Ertuğrul's son Osman I, is the founder of the Ottoman Empire. After the establishment of the Ottoman Empire, he became one of its military commanders, serving Osman.
